title: Premier League Flops of the Week: Who joins Lallana and Huddlestone in our XI from GW29?
text:
1 of 12 Which Premier League players had a weekend to forget? 
Arsenal were victims of a 3-1 thumping at the hands of West Bromwich Albion while Manchester United and Chelsea edged past lesser opponents to pick up all three points. 
Hull City were hammered by a rampant Everton and Sunderland were held to a draw by Burnley, but which stars struggled to impress over the latest round of fixtures? 
Scroll through the gallery above to see which unlucky players make up our Flops of the Week XI from this weekend's batch of Premier League matches. Related articles
